flowchart TD
    %% External Actors
    Human[Human Engineer] -->|Defines Intent, Provides Feedback| API
    AI[AI Agent] -->|Generates Code, Provides Suggestions| API
    ExtUser[External Users / Systems] -->|API Requests| API
    API -->|API Responses| ExtUser

    %% Core Layers
    subgraph Core
        API[API Layer] -->|Requests| Service[Service Layer]
        Service -->|Business Logic| Storage[Storage Layer]
        Storage -->|Read/Write Data| Knowledge[Knowledge Store]
        Knowledge -->|Insights, Learned Patterns| Service
    end

    %% Data Flows (optional)
    style API fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0
    style Service fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32
    style Storage fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ef6c00
    style Knowledge fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#6a1b9a
